com.here.android.mpa.search

Class ContactDetail

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.search.ContactDetail

  • public class ContactDetail
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents detailed information about a contact for a Place.

    For example, if a Place has among its known contacts the phone number 555-1234, use this class to access details about that particular contact's type ("phone") and value ("555-1234").
